
### 建立短碼
POST http://localhost:3000/api/short-urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.google.com"
}

### 查詢短碼資訊
GET http://localhost:3000/api/short-urls/{{code}}

### 短碼轉址
GET http://localhost:3000/{{code}}

### 建立一個無效的網址
POST http://localhost:3000/api/short-urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "this is not a url"
}

### 查詢一個不存在的短碼
GET http://localhost:3000/api/short-urls/nonexistentcode

### 轉址一個不存在的短碼
GET http://localhost:3000/nonexistentcode

### 取得 QR code
GET http://localhost:3000/api/qrcode/{{code}}
